  "sourceCode": "Employer Portal",
  "title": "Brand Event Executive",
  "description": "<p>Do you love creating unforgettable experiences and connecting with people? We’re looking for a <strong>Brand Event Executive</strong> to bring our clients’ brands to life through exciting events and activations.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>What You’ll Do:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Assist in planning and executing brand events, roadshows, and campaigns.</li>\n  <li>Represent the brand and engage with customers face-to-face.</li>\n  <li>Work closely with a supportive team to ensure smooth event operations.</li>\n  <li>Share creative input to make events stand out.</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>What We’re Looking For:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Energetic and outgoing personality.</li>\n  <li>Passion for marketing, branding, and events.</li>\n  <li>Great communication and teamwork skills.</li>\n  <li>No experience required — training provided!</li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Perks:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n  <li>Work with a fun and supportive team (friends who turn into family!).</li>\n  <li>Travel opportunities for regional events.</li>\n  <li>Continuous learning with hands-on training.</li>\n  <li>Clear career growth opportunities.</li>\n</ul>\n<p>If you’re ready to build a career in branding and events while having fun along the way, hit <strong>Apply Now</strong> and join us!</p>",
